filterDefinition.expression: [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VENDOR_NAME] is not null and [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VENDOR_NAME] <>''

queryItem.name: EXPIRAY MONTH
queryItem.expression: extract ( month , [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[CURR_TERMEXPIRY_DATE] )

queryItem.name: EXPIRY QUARTER
queryItem.expression: case extract ( month , [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[CURR_TERMEXPIRY_DATE] ) when 1 then 1 when 2 then 1 when 3 then 1 when 4 then 2 when 5 then 2 when 6 then 2 when 7 then 3 when 8 then 3 when 9 then 3 when 10 then 4 when 11 then 4 when 12 then 4 end

queryItem.name: EXPIRY YEAR
queryItem.expression: extract ( year , [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[CURR_TERMEXPIRY_DATE] )

dbQuery.sql: Select * From [Royalty Netezza - Staging].CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_R as CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_R

queryItem.name: MIN MONTH IN PREV QTR
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARQTR] = (case when extract ( month, current_date ) in (1,2,3) then cast(extract (year, current_date )-1,char(4)) ||'Q4' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (4,5,6) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q1' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (7,8,9) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q2' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (10,11,12) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q3' end) then minimum ( [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARMONTH] for [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARQTR] ) else null end

queryItem.name: MAX MONTH IN PREV QTR
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARQTR] = (case when extract ( month, current_date ) in (1,2,3) then cast(extract (year, current_date )-1,char(4)) ||'Q4' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (4,5,6) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q1' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (7,8,9) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q2' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (10,11,12) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q3' end) then maximum ( [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARMONTH] for [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARQTR] ) else null end

queryItem.name: YEARMONTH_FLAG
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARMONTH] =[Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[MIN MONTH IN PREV QTR] THEN 'start month' WHEN [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARMONTH] =[Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[MAX MONTH IN PREV QTR] THEN 'end month' ELSE [Database Layer].[CYCLEDATES].[YEARMONTH] END

queryItem.name: MIN MONTH IN PREV QTR
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARQTR] = (case when extract ( month, current_date ) in (1,2,3) then cast(extract (year, current_date )-1,char(4)) ||'Q4' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (4,5,6) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q1' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (7,8,9) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q2' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (10,11,12) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q3' end) then minimum ( [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARMONTH] for [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARQTR] ) else null end

queryItem.name: MAX MONTH IN PREV QTR
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARQTR] = (case when extract ( month, current_date ) in (1,2,3) then cast(extract (year, current_date )-1,char(4)) ||'Q4' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (4,5,6) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q1' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (7,8,9) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q2' when extract ( month, current_date ) in (10,11,12) then cast(extract (year, current_date ),char(4))||'Q3' end) then maximum ( [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARMONTH] for [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARQTR] ) else null end

queryItem.name: YEARMONTH_FLAG
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARMONTH] =[Database Layer].[DATES].[MIN MONTH IN PREV QTR] THEN 'start month' WHEN [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARMONTH] =[Database Layer].[DATES].[MAX MONTH IN PREV QTR] THEN 'end month' ELSE [Database Layer].[DATES].[YEARMONTH] END

queryItem.name: REV_SUBTYPE_FIN
queryItem.expression: Case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[REV_TYPE_FIN] ='Blue' and [Database Layer].[ACCOUNTING].[REV_SUBTYPE_FIN]='' Then 'UNKNOWN AT=6' Else [Database Layer].[ACCOUNTING].[REV_SUBTYPE_FIN] End

queryItem.name: AT_customer_type
queryItem.expression: Case When [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[ACTIVITY_TYPE] in ('M','N', 'DMLC', 'L','O','6', 'T', 'W','SASC') then 'COMMERCIAL' When [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[ACTIVITY_TYPE] in ('1','I','2', 'DMLI', '8', 'K','U','CLDI','9','SASI','J') then 'INTERNAL' When [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[ACTIVITY_TYPE] in ('C','R') then 'GREEN' Else '' End

queryItem.name: COMPONENTPN
queryItem.expression: trim([Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN])

queryItem.name: COMPONENTPN_7
queryItem.expression: trim([Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN_7])

queryItem.name: EE_VARIANT
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='ESW' THEN [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN] ELSE NULL END

queryItem.name: ACTIVE
queryItem.expression: if ([Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[CONTRACT_STATUS] ='ACTIVE') then ( 'Y') else ('N')

queryItem.name: AMENDMENT_ACTIVATED_DATE
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[REPLACES_DATE]< cast('2018-10-01',date) then null else [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[REPLACES_DATE] end

queryItem.name: PAYMENT_CYCLE
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_REVENUE] not in ('','NONE') then [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_REVENUE] when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_VOLUMES] not in ('','NONE') then [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_VOLUMES] when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_USAGE] not in ('','NONE') then [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_USAGE] when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_BILLING] not in ('','NONE') then [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_BILLING] when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[FIXED_PAYMENTS] not in ('','NONE') then [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[FIXED_PAYMENTS] end

queryItem.name: PAYMENT_TYPE
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[FIXED_PAYMENTS] not in ('','NONE') and ([Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_VOLUMES] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_USAGE] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_REVENUE] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_BILLING] not in ('','NONE') ) then 'FIXED/VARIABLE' when [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[FIXED_PAYMENTS] not in ('','NONE') then 'FIXED' when ([Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_VOLUMES] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_USAGE] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_REVENUE] not in ('','NONE') OR [Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[VARIABLE_BY_BILLING] not in ('','NONE') ) then 'VARIABLE' else 'PAYMENT TYPE UNDEFINED' end

queryItem.name: RS_ANALYST
queryItem.expression: upper([Database Layer].[CONTRACT].[RS_ANALYST])

queryItem.name: TRANSACTION_TYPE
queryItem.expression: case when ([Database Layer].[DATATYPE].[DATATYPE] = 'VDR') then ('Vol') else ('Rev') end

queryItem.name: GEO
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[COUNTRY].[COUNTRY_NUMBER] ='897' then 'NORTH AMERICA' else [Database Layer].[COUNTRY].[GEO] end

queryItem.name: GEONUM
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[COUNTRY].[COUNTRY_NUMBER] ='897' then 'NA' else [Database Layer].[COUNTRY].[GEONUM] end

queryItem.name: ENTERPR
queryItem.expression: trim( [Database Layer].[CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_R].[ENTERPR] )

queryItem.name: Max Cycle Month
queryItem.expression: maximum ( case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CYCLE_YEAR] =extract(year,current_date) then [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CYCLE_MONTH] end for report )

queryItem.name: Max Month
queryItem.expression: maximum ( case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[YEAR] =extract(year,current_date) then [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[MONTH] end for report )

queryItem.name: PILLAR_AIW
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[DATATYPE].[DATATYPE] ='AIW' then [Database Layer].[PART].[PILLAR] else null end

queryItem.name: PRODID
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='DSW' AND [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN] ='' THEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PRODID] WHEN[Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='DSW' AND [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN] <>'' THEN [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN] WHEN[Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='ESW' THEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PRODID] END

queryItem.name: PRODID_7
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='DSW' AND [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN_7] ='' THEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PRODID_7] WHEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='DSW' AND [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN_7] <>'' THEN [Database Layer].[COMPONENT].[COMPONENTPN_7] WHEN[Database Layer].[PART].[PARTTYPE] ='ESW' THEN [Database Layer].[PART].[PRODID_7] ELSE 'ERROR' END

queryItem.name: ProdID_Variant
queryItem.expression: [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[PRODID_7] || ' - ' || [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[EE_VARIANT]

queryItem.name: CONTRACT_VOLUME
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[ACTIVITY].[ACTIVITY_STATUS] ='I' or ([Database Layer].[ACTIVITY].[ACTIVITY_STATUS] ='' and [Database Layer].[LICENSE].[LICENSE_TYPE] ='MLC') then [Database Layer].[PAYMENTFACT].[CONTRACT_VOLUME] else 0 end

queryItem.name: E/R
queryItem.expression: IF ( [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[Revenue] <>0 ) THEN ( [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[ROYALTY_PAYMENT] / [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[Revenue] ) ELSE ( null )

queryItem.name: rev_usd
queryItem.expression: IF ( [Database Layer].[DATATYPE].[DATATYPE] ='AIW' ) THEN ( [Database Layer].[PAYMENTFACT].[CONTRACT_REV_USD] *(-1) ) ELSE ( null )

queryItem.name: contract_rev(M$)
queryItem.expression: [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CONTRACT_REV_USD] /1000000

queryItem.name: royalty_payment(M$)
queryItem.expression: [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[ROYALTY_PAYMENT] /1000000

queryItem.name: VOLUME
queryItem.expression: case when [Database Layer].[DATATYPE].[DATATYPE] ='VDR' and [Database Layer].[ACTIVITY].[ACTIVITY_STATUS] <> 'I' then 0 else [Database Layer].[PAYMENTFACT].[VOLUME] end

queryItem.name: Geo_flag
queryItem.expression: case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[IOT] <> '<All>' then 'Y' else 'N' end

queryItem.name: Royalty_rev_flg
queryItem.expression: case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[RATE] >0 then 'Y' else 'N' end

queryItem.name: PERCENTAGE_RATE
queryItem.expression: case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[RATE_TYPE] ='PERCENT' then [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[RATE] else null end

queryItem.name: TIER
queryItem.expression: [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[MIN_TIER] ||':'||[Modelling Layer].[Payments].[MAX_TIER]

queryItem.name: FIXED_VOL_RATE
queryItem.expression: case when [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[RATE_TYPE] ='FIXED' then [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[RATE] else null end

filter.name: Rolling 12 Months
filter.expression: ( [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[YEAR] =extract(year,current_date)-1 and [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[MONTH] >=[Modelling Layer].[Payments].[Max Month] ) or [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[YEAR] =extract(year,current_date)

filter.name: Rolling 12 Months(Cycle)
filter.expression: ( [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CYCLE_YEAR] =extract(year,current_date)-1 and [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CYCLE_MONTH] >=[Modelling Layer].[Payments].[Max Cycle Month] ) or [Modelling Layer].[Payments].[CYCLE_YEAR] =extract(year,current_date)
